sts/fxpodcast-the-hunger-games/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-04-25 |archive-date=2012-04-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120420053607/http://www.fxguide.com/fxpodcasts/fxpodcast-the-hunger-games/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。」

儘管勞倫斯在拍攝前已是20歲，比她的角色年長了4歲<ref>{{cite news|first=Keith|last=Staskiewicz|url=http://popwatch.ew.com/2011/03/17/jennifer-lawrence-too-old-katniss-hunger-games/|title='Hunger Games': Is Jennifer Lawrence the Katniss of your dreams?|work=Entertainment Weekly|date=2011-03-17|accessdate=2012-02-07|archive-date=2012-09-20|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AoetzJAg?url=http://popwatch.ew.com/2011/03/17/jennifer-lawrence-too-old-katniss-hunger-games/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，柯林斯說角色的需要「有一定程度的成熟與力量」，並指女演員成熟的比年輕的好<ref>{{cite news|first=Karen|last=Valby|url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2011/03/17/hunger-games-gary-ross-jennifer-lawrence/|title='Hunger Games' director Gary Ross talks about 'the easiest casting decision of my life''|work=Entertainment Weekly|date=2011-03-17|accessdate=2011-03-21|archive-date=2012-09-20|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AoeudJCD?url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2011/03/17/hunger-games-gary-ross-jennifer-lawrence/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她補充說勞倫斯是「唯一一個能捕捉到我寫在小說中角色的神髓」，並且指她有「演繹凱妮絲的每個重要和必須的質素」<ref>{{cite news|first=Darren|last=Franich|url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2011/03/21/hunger-games-suzanne-collins-jennifer-lawrence/|title='Hunger Games': Suzanne Collins talks Jennifer Lawrence as Katniss|work=Entertainment Weekly|date=2011-03-21|accessdate=2011-03-21|archive-date=2013-06-05|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6H8jYQMyd?url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2011/03/21/hunger-games-suzanne-collins-jennifer-lawrence/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。勞倫斯作為這小說的書迷，花了三天的時間來接受角色，她最初被電影製作的規模嚇倒<ref name="HReporter2.7.12" /><ref name="brand-new">{{cite news|first=Steven|last=Galloway|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/hunger-games-jennifer-lawrence-katniss-286282|title=Jennifer Lawrence: A Brand-New Superstar|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2012-02-01|accessdate=2012-02-07|archive-date=2013-06-05|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6H8jX7lkA?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/hunger-games-jennifer-lawrence-katniss-286282|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

飾演男主角比德·梅爾拉克方面，除了[[喬許·哈卻森|喬許·哈契遜]]以外，爭奪者還包括[[亞歷山大·路德韋格|亞歷山大·路德韋格]] (他後來飾演卡圖)、[[亨特·帕里什|亨特·帕里什]]、[[盧卡斯·提爾|盧卡斯·提爾]]和[[埃文·彼得斯|埃文·彼得斯]]<ref name="borys">{{cite news|first=Borys|last=Kit|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/lionsgate-testing-actors-star-hunger-171575|title=Lionsgate Testing Actors to Star in 'Hunger Games' Opposite Jennifer Lawrence|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2011-03-25|accessdate=2011-04-06|archive-date=2011-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110426123715/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/lionsgate-testing-actors-star-hunger-171575|dead-url=no}}</ref>。對於飾演蓋爾·霍桑的演員，包括[[大衛·亨利|大衛·亨利]]、{{tsl|en|Drew Roy|德魯羅伊}}及[[羅比·艾梅爾|羅比·艾梅爾]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/lionsgate-testing-actors-star-hunger-171575 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-04-26 |archive-date=2011-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110426123715/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/lionsgate-testing-actors-star-hunger-171575 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年4月，[[約翰·C·萊利|約翰·C·韋利]]與[[獅門娛樂|獅門娛樂]]的會談，討論飾演黑密契·阿勃納西一角<ref name="Reilly">{{cite news|first=Claude|last=Brodesser-Akner|url=http://www.vulture.com/2011/04/john_c_reilly_in_talks_to_play.html|title=John C. Reilly Being Offered Role of Haymitch in The Hunger Games|work=[[New_York_(magazine)|New York]]|date=2011-04-22|accessdate=2011-04-25|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120162458/https://www.vulture.com/2011/04/john_c_reilly_in_talks_to_play.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在隨後的一個月，獅門娛樂宣布此角色由[[奧斯卡|奧斯卡]]提名人[[伍迪·哈里森|伍迪·哈里森]]飾演<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/woody-harrelson-cast-as-haymitch-187194 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-04-26 |archive-date=2011-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110511222452/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/woody-harrelson-cast-as-haymitch-187194 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其他角色方面，凱薩·富萊克曼是由[[史丹利·特治|史丹利·特治]]飾演，[[陶比·瓊斯|陶比·瓊斯]]飾演克勞帝亞斯·坦普史密斯，[[藍尼·克羅維茲|藍尼·克羅維茲]]飾演秦納。2011年5月下旬，史諾總统的角色落實由多項[[金球獎|金球獎]]得主[[當奴·修打蘭|當奴·修打蘭]]飾演<ref>{{cite news|url=http://screenrant.com/hunger-games-donald-sutherland-president-snow-sandy-117769/|title=''The Hunger Games'' casts Donald Sutherland as President Snow|publisher=Screenrant|date=2012-05-31|accessdate=2012-04-27|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303200104/http://screenrant.com/hunger-games-donald-sutherland-president-snow-sandy-117769/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 拍攝 ===
[[File:Bridal_Veil_Falls_DuPont_State_Forest.jpg|thumb]]{{tsl|en|DuPont State Forest|杜邦國家森林公園}}的{{tsl|en|Bridal Veil Falls (DuPont State Forest)|新娘面紗瀑布}}。]]
2010年11月，[[蓋瑞·羅斯|蓋瑞·羅斯]]成為此電影的導演<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ew.com/article/2011/01/06/hunger-games-exclusive-gary-ross |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-04-27 |archive-date=2021-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421045552/https://ew.com/article/2011/01/06/hunger-games-exclusive-gary-ross/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，{{tsl|en|Fireman's Fund Insurance Company|消防員基金保險公司}}為製作保險承保，但作為承保過程的一部分，他們堅持為隱患進行一個全面的風險分析，如各不相同任性的箭、毒藤、熊、昆蟲、以及在急速的流水中追逐<ref name="morrissey">Janet Morrissey (March 24, 2012). [http://www.nytimes.com/2012/03/25/business/insuring-hollywood-against-falls-but-not-flops.html "Insuring Hollywood Against Falls (but Not Flops)"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/03/25/business/insuring-hollywood-against-falls-but-not-flops.html |date=20210525043319 }}. ''The New York Times''. BU1.</ref>。

[[珍妮佛·勞倫斯|珍妮佛·勞倫斯]]把自己金色的頭髮染成凱妮絲的深色<ref>{{cite web|first=Tom|last=Ayres|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a321116/jennifer-lawrence-unaware-of-hunger-games-hate.html|title=Jennifer Lawrence 'unaware of Hunger Games hate'|publisher=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]]|date=2011-05-23|accessdate=2011-12-18|archive-date=2013-06-05|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6H8jZ9NQM?url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a321116/jennifer-lawrence-unaware-of-hunger-games-hate.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，她還接受全面的訓練，來塑造角色的身型，訓練包括[[射箭|射箭]]、[[攀石|攀石]]和爬樹、[[格鬥|格鬥]]、[[跑步|跑步]]、[[跑酷|跑酷]]及[[瑜伽|瑜伽]]<ref>{{cite web|first=Jennifer|last=Still|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a321543/jennifer-lawrence-hunger-games-training-fun.html|title=Jennifer Lawrence: 'Hunger Games training fun'|publisher=Digital Spy|date=2011-05-26|accessdate=2011-12-18|archive-date=2013-03-13|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6F5JPSmrq?url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a321543/jennifer-lawrence-hunger-games-training-fun.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而在她為期六周的訓練階段中，最後那天出了個意外，她全速跑步時撞向牆壁，但傷勢並不嚴重。其他為電影把頭髮染深的包括飾演比德·梅爾拉克的[[喬許·哈卻森|喬許·哈契遜]]和飾演蓋爾·霍桑的[[連恩·漢斯沃|連恩·漢斯沃]]<ref name="#2">{{Cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/hunger-games-jennifer-lawrence-josh-hutcherson-liam-hemsworth-gary-ross-twilight-285957 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2012-03-20 |archive-date=2017-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170709235352/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/hunger-games-jennifer-lawrence-josh-hutcherson-liam-hemsworth-gary-ross-twilight-285957 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[獅門娛樂|獅門娛樂]]聘請了弓箭手 (以及[[奧運會|奧運會]]銅牌得主) {{tsl|en|Khatuna Lorig|哈圖娜-洛裡格}}教勞倫斯怎樣射箭<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/03/25/business/insuring-hollywood-against-falls-but-not-flops.html?_r=0 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-04-27 |archive-date=2020-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200421115627/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/03/25/business/insuring-hollywood-against-falls-but-not-flops.html?_r=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2011年5月，主要拍攝以初步預算的$75,000,000美元開拍<ref name="#3">{{Cite web |url=http://www.slashfilm.com/hunger-games-casting-lavinia-avox-venia-flavius-played-relative-unknowns/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2012-06-14 |archive-date=2021-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226060738/https://www.slashfilm.com/hunger-games-casting-lavinia-avox-venia-flavius-played-relative-unknowns/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，拍攝主要在[[北卡羅來納州|北卡羅來納州]]西部[[特蘭西瓦尼亞縣_(北卡羅來納州)|特蘭西瓦尼亞縣]]的布裡瓦德鎮 (Brevard) 附近開拍<ref name="#3"/><ref name="SlashFilm">{{cite web|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/hunger-games-casting-lavinia-avox-venia-flavius-played-relative-unknowns/|title=More 'Hunger Games' Casting: Lavinia the Avox, Venia and Flavius Played By Relative Unknowns|last=Lussier|first=Germain|publisher={{tsl|en|/Film|/Film}}|date=2011-05-27|accessdate=2011-05-27|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226060738/https://www.slashfilm.com/hunger-games-casting-lavinia-avox-venia-flavius-played-relative-unknowns/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，大多數外景是攝於[[亨德森縣_(北卡羅來納州)|亨德森縣]]與特蘭西瓦尼亞縣之間的{{tsl|en|DuPont State Forest|杜邦國家森林公園}}，公園佔地40平方公里，攝製隊在該處拍攝第11區暴亂的場面<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1681105/hunger-games-avox-cut.jhtml |title='Hunger Games' Director Gary Ross 'Sorry' About Cuts' There was no room for [Avox subplot] in the storytelling, unfortunately,' director tells MTV News. |access-date=2015-04-27 |archive-date=2012-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121204110817/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1681105/hunger-games-avox-cut.jhtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由於部分拍攝時間表的緊密，這部電影是以[[菲林|菲林]]膠卷拍攝而非數碼制式。導演羅斯在《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》的訪問時說，「我不想經常有數碼拍攝帶來技術問題的風險—我們根本負擔不起任何的延誤<ref>{{cite news |url=http://artsbeat.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/03/30/gary-ross-answers-reader-questions-about-the-hunger-games/ |title=Gary Ross Answers Reader Questions About 'The Hunger Games{{'-}} |first=Mekado |last=Murphy |work=The New York Times |date=2012-03-30 |accessdate=2012-03-31 |archive-date=2012-05-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120504140440/http://artsbeat.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/03/30/gary-ross-answers-reader-questions-about-the-hunger-games/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>」。拍攝於2011年9月15日完成<ref name=lionsgate>{{cite press release | url=http://www.lionsgatepublicity.com/epk/thehungergames/ | title=The Hunger Games | date=2012-03-03 | accessdate=2012-03-03 | publisher=[[Lions_Gate_Entertainment|Lions Gate Entertainment]] | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120103121025/http://lionsgatepublicity.com/epk/thehungergames/ | archivedate=2012-01-03 }}</ref>，最終預算報告在$90,000,000美元至$100,000,000美元之間，補貼後減少了$78,000,000美元<ref name="#2"/>，[[史蒂文·索德伯格|史蒂文·索德伯格]]擔任第二單元導演<ref name="#4">{{cite web |author=Adam Chitwood |title=Steven Soderbergh is Directing Second Unit on The Hunger Games |url=http://collider.com/steven-soderbergh-hunger-games/107523/ |publisher=Collider |date=2011-08-04 |accessdate=2012-01-08 |archive-date=2011-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110816141328/http://collider.com/steven-soderbergh-hunger-games/107523/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="#4"/>。

實際上所有攝影製作都在[[北卡羅萊納州|北卡羅萊納州]]進行，[[獅門娛樂|獅門娛樂]]收到當地州政府的$8,000,000美元稅收抵免。據福布斯雜誌估計，國營經濟從製作獲得了高達6,000萬美元，有5,000人獲聘為群眾演員、劇組工作人員及支援人員<ref name="forbes-nc">{{cite news|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/kellyphillipserb/2012/03/19/will-nc-win-the-hunger-games/|title=Will NC win the Hunger Games?|accessdate=2012-04-30|date=2012-03-19|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111230839/https://www.forbes.com/sites/kellyphillipserb/2012/03/19/will-nc-win-the-hunger-games/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。大部分的戶外場景，包括12區的郊外和競技場，那些都是攝於杜邦國家森林公園；那些{{tsl|en|Little River (North Carolina)|北卡羅萊納州河流}}，以及當中的瀑布，為拍攝走過競技場的場景<ref name="cnn-nc">{{cite news|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2012/03/26/travel/hunger-games-travel/index.html|title=North Carolina lures ''Hunger Games'' fans|publisher=CNN|accessdate=2012-04-30|date=2012-03-27|archive-date=2012-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120430143629/http://edition.cnn.com/2012/03/26/travel/hunger-games-travel/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>：製作團隊在{{tsl|en|Triple Falls (DuPont State Forest)|三重瀑布}}頂部建立了一條橫跨行人道讓勞倫斯飾演的凱妮絲能在急流中奔跑<ref name="newsobserver-nc">{{cite news|url=http://www.newsobserver.com/2012/03/18/1936882/hunger-games-films-impact-immediate.html|title=Hunger Games Film's immediate impact across NC|date=2012-03-18|publisher=[[News_&_Observer|News & Observer]]|accessdate=2012-04-30|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120428041040/http://www.newsobserver.com/2012/03/18/1936882/hunger-games-films-impact-immediate.html|archivedate=2012-04-28}}</ref>。

許多都市和內部地區，在國會大廈和其他地方，都是在{{tsl|en|Shelby, North Carolina|謝爾比市}}和[[夏洛特_(北卡羅來納州)|夏洛特市]]拍攝的；其他場景就是在[[阿什維爾|阿什維爾]]取景拍攝的。導演羅斯與美工設計師菲爾·梅西在設計國會大廈的建築時，他們借鑒了1939年的[[紐約|紐約]][[世界博覽會|世界博覽會]]和包括[[天安門廣場|天安門廣場]]和[[紅場|紅場]]的政治權力象徵，以希望「設置為未來但有它自己過去的感覺...這是一種歡慶的和誘人的以及放縱的和墮落的，但它也有那種權力背後的可能性<ref name="cinemablend">{{cite web|url=http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Hunger-Games-Director-Gary-Ross-Talks-Handling-Phenomenon-30085.html|title=Hunger Games Director Gary Ross Talks Handling The Phenomenon|date=2012-03-21|first=Eric|last=Eisenberg|accessdate=2012-05-08|publisher=Cinemablend|archive-date=2021-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420110100/https://www.cinemablend.com/new/Hunger-Games-Director-Gary-Ross-Talks-Handling-Phenomenon-30085.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="messinaset">{{cite video|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5SR4CrHw9Eo|title=Hunger Games: Philip Messina|accessdate=2012-05-08|archive-date=2020-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200421115704/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5SR4CrHw9Eo|dead-url=no}}</ref> 」。對於凱妮絲在第12區的鄰里，製作團隊找到{{tsl|en|Henry River Mill Village|亨利河水磨小村}}，導演羅斯說「只是為電影完美地工作來喚起場景的感覺」；梅西納解釋指，「我們原本談到可能要建一個房子和隔壁的房子的門面並重新調整它，也許可以做一些CG延伸...我們最終找到一整個廢棄的水磨鎮...這絕對是完美的」<ref name="messinaset" />。

至於服裝設計，{{tsl|en|Judianna Makovsky|茱迪安娜·馬科夫斯基}}與她的團隊看過很多50年代煤炭開採地區美國感覺的照片<ref name="vogue">{{cite web|url=http://www.vogue.com/873551/dressing-the-hunger-games-costume-designer-judianna-makovsky|title=Dressing The Hunger Games: Costume Designer Judianna Makovsky|date=2012-03-19|first=Molly|last=Creeden|accessdate=2015-01-30|publisher=Vogue|archive-date=2015-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150130152757/http://www.vogue.com/873551/dressing-the-hunger-games-costume-designer-judianna-makovsky|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當時的構思是想為每個角色創造獨特的服飾來強烈區分國會與地區人民 <ref name="glosty">{{cite web|url=http://www.glosty.co/article/869062697185/hunger-games-inspired-fashion-learn-how-to-dress-like-katniss-and-effie|title=Hunger Games Inspired Fashion: Learn How to Dress Like Katniss and Effie|date=2015-01-30|first=Clement|last=Ana|accessdate=2015-01-30|publisher=Glosty|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305080346/http://glosty.co/article/869062697185/hunger-games-inspired-fashion-learn-how-to-dress-like-katniss-and-effie|dead-url=no}}</ref>。灰色和藍色是地區盛行的色調，而國會大廈的人都會選擇色彩明亮誇張的帽子、花、褶邊、粉末狀白色和眉毛很少甚至沒有眉毛的面孔<ref name="vogue" />。

=== 音樂 ===
==== 原聲碟 ====
《飢餓遊戲》的原聲專輯包含的歌曲，靈感來源自電影；當中只有三首歌曲出現在電影的片尾字幕部分，歌曲分別是：《亞伯拉罕的女兒 <small>(Abraham's Daughter)</small>》、《安然無恙 <small>(Safe & Sound)</small>》以及《大國降臨 <small>(Kingdom Come)</small>》<ref name="wsj soundtrack">{{cite news|first=Ethan|last=Smith|url=http://online.wsj.com/news/articles/SB10001424052702303812904577295854005605494|title='Hunger Games' Steps in to Save the Soundtrack|work=The Wall Street Journal|date=2012-03-21|accessdate=2012-03-21|archive-date=2013-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131111170723/http://online.wsj.com/news/articles/SB10001424052702303812904577295854005605494|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影的原聲專輯首支單曲，由[[泰勒·斯威夫特|泰勒·斯威夫特]]主唱，跟二人樂隊{{tsl|en|The Civil Wars|內戰(樂隊)}}伴唱的《[[安然無恙|安然無恙]]》，歌曲於2011年12月23日發布<ref>{{cite web |first=Marc |last=Hogan |title=Listen to Taylor Swift's 'Hunger Games' Ballad |url=http://www.spin.com/articles/listen-taylor-swifts-hunger-games-ballad |work=[[Spin_(雜誌)|Spin]] |date=2011-12-23 |accessdate=2011-12-23 |archive-date=2013-03-13 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6F5JSGm1W?url=http://www.spin.com/articles/listen-taylor-swifts-hunger-games-ballad |dead-url=no }}</ref>，它在發布的12小時內登上[[iTunes|iTunes]]的總排行榜榜首，而歌曲的MV於2012年2月13日發布。除了泰勒·斯威夫特與內戰的歌曲外，原聲專輯也有歌曲由{{tsl|en|The Decemberists|十二月黨}}、[[拱廊之火|拱廊之火]]、二人組合{{tsl|en|The Secret Sisters|秘密姊妹花}}、[[米蘭達·蘭伯特|米蘭達·蘭伯特]]與{{tsl|en|Pistol Annies|安妮絲手槍樂隊}}合唱的歌<ref name="HungerMusic" />，還有{{tsl|en|Neko Case|內蔻·凱斯}}，{{tsl|en|Kid Cudi|小孩安迪}}<ref name="HungerMusic">{{cite web |author=Emily Tseng |title="The Hunger Games" Soundtrack Actually Looks Pretty Good |url=http://blogs.dailyprincetonian.com/intersections/2012/02/13/the-hunger-games-soundtrack-actually-looks-pretty-good/ |work=[[The_Daily_Princetonian|The Daily Princetonian]] |date=2012-02-13 |accessdate=2012-02-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130121073547/http://blogs.dailyprincetonian.com/intersections/2012/02/13/the-hunger-games-soundtrack-actually-looks-pretty-good/ |archivedate=2013-01-21 }}</ref>、[[奧斯卡獎|奧斯卡獎]]得主{{tsl|en|Glen Hansard|格倫·漢塞德}}<ref name="HungerMusic" />、三人組合{{tsl|en|The Low Anthem|低頌歌}}<ref name="HungerMusic" />、{{tsl|en|Punch Brothers|衝撞兄弟樂隊}}<ref name="HungerMusic" />、[[Birdy_(歌手)|Birdy]]<ref name="HungerMusic" />、[[魔力紅|Maroon 5]]、{{tsl|en|Jayme Dee|傑姆·迪伊}}<ref name="HungerMusic" />和{{tsl|en|Carolina Chocolate Drops|卡羅萊納黑人少女樂隊}} <ref name="HungerMusic" />。原聲專輯於2012年3月20日發布<ref name="nypost">{{cite web|url=http://nypost.com/2012/03/16/hunger-games-soundtrack-already-a-hit/|title='Hunger Games' soundtrack already a hit|last=Atkinson|first=Claire|date=2012-03-16|work=[[New_York_Post|New York Post]]|accessdate=2013-12-11|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201181141/https://nypost.com/2012/03/16/hunger-games-soundtrack-already-a-hit/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，專輯曲目在2012年2月13日於[[iTunes|iTunes]]上披露，並於翌日(14日)發布第二首單曲《一個發動機 <small>(One Engine)</small>》。[[珍妮佛·勞倫斯|珍妮佛·勞倫斯]]主唱的《芸的搖籃曲 <small>(Rue's Lullaby)</small>》並沒有收錄其中。該專輯首度榮登[[告示牌200大專輯榜|告示牌200大專輯榜]]第一位，推出首周已售出175,000張。這是繼[[米高·積遜|米高·積遜]]的《[[This_Is_It_(迈克尔·杰克逊专辑)|This Is It]]》首發即登冠軍的記錄後的第一張專輯，這是[[告示牌200大專輯榜|告示牌200大專輯榜]]的史上榮登冠軍的16張原聲碟之一。

